'''鲍比·雷·“鮑伯”·艾塞瑞吉'''（{{lang-en|'''Bobby Ray "Bob" Etheridge'''}}，{{bd|1941年|8月7日||}}）是[[美国|美国]]的一名[[民主党_(美国)|民主党]]籍政治家，他在1997年至2011年间曾是北卡罗来纳州第二选区的[[美国众议院|众议员]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/12/31/bob-etheridge-farm_n_4523233.html |title=Huffington Post/Associated Press |access-date=2016-09-11 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304124003/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/12/31/bob-etheridge-farm_n_4523233.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>2012年时他曾为民主黨的北卡罗来纳州州长候选人，不过没有选上。<ref name="abclocal.go.com">{{Cite news|url=http://abclocal.go.com/wtvd/story?section=news/politics&id=8529264|title=Former Rep. Bob Etheridge to run for governor|date=February 12, 2012|work=ABC 11|accessdate=February 12, 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130718183528/http://abclocal.go.com/wtvd/story?section=news%2Fpolitics&id=8529264|archive-date=2013-07-18|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

== 生平 ==
艾塞瑞吉出生在[[北卡罗来纳州|北卡罗来纳州]]的[[桑普森縣_(北卡羅萊納州)|桑普森县]]，他在高中时为篮球校队。他在1965年至1967年曾于[[美国陆军|美国陆军]]服役。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-srv/elections/2004/candidates/22216/ |title=Bob Etheridge (D). |access-date=2016-09-11 |archive-date=2016-04-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160408183320/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-srv/elections/2004/candidates/22216/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>艾塞瑞吉亦经营[[煙草種植|烟草业]]和[[五金店|五金行件商店]]。

=== 政治生涯 ===
[[File:Bob_Etheridge_and_family_1992.jpg|thumb]]
艾塞瑞吉在1978年即當選[[北卡罗来纳州众议院|北卡罗来纳州众议院]]議員。<ref name="official biography">{{Cite web|url=http://etheridge.house.gov/Biography/|title=Biography|publisher=United States House of Representatives|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100608223034/http://etheridge.house.gov/Biography/|archivedate=2010-06-08}}</ref>1996年，艾塞瑞吉在北卡罗莱纳州的第二国会选区参选，并击败了寻求连任的共和党籍议员大卫·芬德布克，得票率约53%-46%。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ourcampaigns.com/RaceDetail.html?RaceID=29637 |title=http://www.ourcampaigns.com/RaceDetail.html? |access-date=2016-09-11 |archive-date=2018-10-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181023234247/https://www.ourcampaigns.com/RaceDetail.html?RaceID=29637 |dead-url=no }}</ref>1998年，他连任第二次，得票率约57％。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ourcampaigns.com/RaceDetail.html?RaceID=30798 |title=http://www.ourcampaigns.com/RaceDetail.html? |access-date=2016-09-11 |archive-date=2018-10-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181023200124/https://www.ourcampaigns.com/RaceDetail.html?RaceID=30798 |dead-url=no }}</ref>2000年连任第3次時得票率约58％。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ourcampaigns.com/RaceDetail.html?RaceID=538 |title=http://www.ourcampaigns.com/RaceDetail.html? |access-date=2016-09-11 |archive-date=2018-10-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181023234401/https://www.ourcampaigns.com/RaceDetail.html?RaceID=538 |dead-url=no }}</ref>之後2002到2008年，他的得票率从来没有低于65％。

2010年艾塞瑞吉面临了强大的敌手——共和党提名的[[勒妮·埃爾姆斯|勒妮·埃爾姆斯]]。她以49.5%-48.7%的得票率击败艾塞瑞吉。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ourcampaigns.com/RaceDetail.html?RaceID=500885 |title=http://www.ourcampaigns.com/RaceDetail.html? |access-date=2016-09-11 |archive-date=2020-05-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200525214738/https://www.ourcampaigns.com/RaceDetail.html?RaceID=500885 |dead-url=no }}</ref>艾塞瑞吉认为这结果有争议，并要求重新计票。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://thehill.com/blogs/ballot-box/house-races/128993-still-trailing-rep-etheridge-calls-for-a-recount-|title=Still trailing, Rep. etheridge calls for a recount|accessdate=2010-11-13|date=November 12, 2010|last=Miller|first=Sean J.|work=The Hill|archive-date=2019-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190410201635/https://thehill.com/blogs/ballot-box/house-races/128993-still-trailing-rep-etheridge-calls-for-a-recount-|dead-url=no}}</ref>19日，结果表明埃尔姆斯赢了1483张票。当天晚些时候，艾塞瑞吉承认了选举。
