=== 参选州长 ===
2012年2月，艾塞瑞吉代表民主黨競選北卡罗莱纳州的州長。<ref name="abclocal.go.com">{{Cite news|url=http://abclocal.go.com/wtvd/story?section=news/politics&id=8529264|title=Former Rep. Bob Etheridge to run for governor|date=February 12, 2012|work=ABC 11|accessdate=February 12, 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130718183528/http://abclocal.go.com/wtvd/story?section=news%2Fpolitics&id=8529264|archive-date=2013-07-18|dead-url=yes}}</ref>但是他敗給共和黨的[[帕特·麥克克羅里|帕特·麥克克羅里]]，沒有選上。<ref>[http://projects.newsobserver.com/under_the_dome/pittsboro_mayor_named_new_democratic_party_chairman News & Observer: Pittsboro mayor named new Democratic party chairman] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130615004302/http://projects.newsobserver.com/under_the_dome/pittsboro_mayor_named_new_democratic_party_chairman |date=2013-06-15 }}</ref>

